<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900906-0120</DOCNO><DOCID>900906-0120.</DOCID><HL>   Horn andamp; Hardart Sells Unit</HL><DATE>09/06/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   HOR</CO><IN>RESTAURANTS, FAST-FOOD, CATERING (RES)TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)</IN><LP>   NEW YORK -- Horn andamp; Hardart Co. closed the sale of itsBojangles chicken-restaurant chain to a group includingSienna Holdings, a closely held Los Angeles investment firm.   In return for Bojangles, Horn andamp; Hardart received $20million of its 14% senior subordinated debentures that thegroup held. The group also assumed $4 million of liabilitiesand capital leases.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>